      "x": 80,
      "y": 425,
      "width": 580,
      "height": 56,
      "text": "Max Cycles (1-50 slider)  •  Fix Severity Threshold (CRITICAL/HIGH/MEDIUM/LOW)\nCore Agent toggles: Explorer, UX Reviewer, Consolidator, Code Simplifier\nDomain streams: UI, Backend, Database, Docs (each enables Analyst + Fixer pair)\nOther: Auto-approve, Infinite sessions, Worktree isolation",
